  "text": "Peripheral blood (PB) samples were collected from healthy individuals and CML patients from June 1998 throughout December 2001. Patients who carried more than 30% blast cells in bone marrow were included in the group of blastic crisis (52.98% Ϯ 11.96%, n ϭ 11) and those who carried less than 30% blast cells in bone marrow were included in the group of chronic phase (11.40% Ϯ 1.62%, n ϭ 21). RNA and gDNA were extracted by standard procedures as described previously. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ",
